### ðŸ“Œ [DevOps]

**What it is:**
DevOps is about automating and streamlining the software delivery process. It bridges development and operations to enable fast, reliable releases.

**Core Topics:**

* CI/CD Pipelines
* Containerization (Docker)
* Orchestration (Kubernetes)
* Infrastructure as Code (Terraform)
* Monitoring & Logging
* Cloud Services (AWS, Azure, GCP)





### ðŸ“Œ [Fullstack Development]

**What it is:**
Fullstack developers handle both frontend and backend development. They are capable of building complete web applications from scratch.

**Core Topics:**

* HTML, CSS, JavaScript
* Frontend Frameworks (React, Angular, etc.)
* Backend Languages and Frameworks (Node.js, Django, etc.)
* Databases & APIs
* DevOps Basics
* Version Control & Deployment


